{"tid":1590244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9.29 10.1唔好齋舉美國旗 要舉舉萬國旗","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T10:02:22.000Z","uid":212731,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd493134e7eb2c8139f6cf88cd1569e5a504fa7f","tid":1590244,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"係舉就舉萬國旗<br />\n唔好齋偏心舉發達國家既旗<br />\n舉多d拉非亞 東歐 波羅的海 特別係受共產黨/中國壓迫既國家既旗<br />\n<br />\n一黎減少不親美國國家人民既反感(拉丁美洲)<br />\n二黎又可以connect更多國家人民既力量<br />\n三黎可以make noise<br />\n四黎畀人覺得香港人唔只淨係識appealing發達國家 亦都會關心弱勢國家 爭取到更多國際同情同支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連結拉非亞(農村包圍城市國際版)依個策略中共最撚擅長 當年中共入到聯合國都係因為第三世界國家既票數夠多<br />\n<br />\n我地學識活用大多數弱勢國家既力量 幾個小國團結起黎會係一個龐大既力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa5e21cbb6321b69145df4a192f68715f068d83","tid":1590244,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"53099fca26bfebda49b09ae6207a7fc2af882d66","tid":1590244,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2551dde6c3c80c17eedcdfb242cb8ab118dd066c","tid":1590244,"uid":36245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGUDn1t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGUDn1t.png&h=d3e1d8e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"831b518f35a808fe8958c28802b310bee81351ff","tid":1590244,"uid":